heading: Photocollage.
general-note: Here are entered works on collage consisting primarily of photographs or reproductions of photographs from magazines, newspapers, etc. Works on combining in a single photographic composition elements from various sources by techniques such as taking a number of exposures on the same negative, or superimposing or juxtaposing negatives to form a composite print, as well as collections of such photographs are entered under. Photomontage..
